      "content": "coconut water sounds good. i already drank some but my arm feels kinda tingly too, like it's falling asleep but it won't wake up. and honestly im kinda confused about where i am for a second. do u think i should take some aspirin or something to help with the headache? i just want to sleep it off and feel better by morning.",
